01:28:55.460 --> 01:28:58.730
I have a question for
Professor Wrangham.

01:28:58.730 --> 01:29:02.560
I'm just trying to work
out how Mitochondrial Eve

01:29:02.560 --> 01:29:06.650
and Y-chromosome Adam could
be alive in different times.

01:29:06.650 --> 01:29:10.040
So it seems to me that one
solution, and the obvious one,

01:29:10.040 --> 01:29:15.690
but probably not the likely one,
is that Eve was messing around,

01:29:15.690 --> 01:29:18.440
so that she would have had
children with four, six, eight,

01:29:18.440 --> 01:29:21.620
who knows how many different
men, who would have carried on.

01:29:21.620 --> 01:29:25.590
Another one would be,
no, Mitochondrial Eve

01:29:25.590 --> 01:29:26.930
is the wrong person to look at.

01:29:26.930 --> 01:29:33.330
There was a Eve who had
children with an Adam.

01:29:33.330 --> 01:29:38.960
And all her female
descendants died out,

01:29:38.960 --> 01:29:42.470
except for one line 80,000
years later or something.

01:29:42.470 --> 01:29:45.860
Could you comment on whether
Adam and Eve would have

01:29:45.860 --> 01:29:49.580
been alive at the same time?

01:29:49.580 --> 01:29:54.260
Well, as I said, I mean, 100,000
years could separate them.

01:29:54.260 --> 01:29:57.890
But I don't think you have to
point too much to Mitochondrial

01:29:57.890 --> 01:29:59.690
Eve herself--

01:29:59.690 --> 01:30:02.540
her daughters, her
granddaughters, and so on.

01:30:02.540 --> 01:30:05.690
I mean, it just
happened that the males

01:30:05.690 --> 01:30:10.820
with whom this lineage
were producing babies

01:30:10.820 --> 01:30:14.870
were males who themselves were
remarkably diverse in terms

01:30:14.870 --> 01:30:17.500
of their origins.

01:30:17.500 --> 01:30:20.180
It maybe happened because the
females were moving around

01:30:20.180 --> 01:30:21.380
into different areas.

01:30:21.380 --> 01:30:24.220
It maybe because the
males were moving around.

01:30:24.220 --> 01:30:28.760
But there's nothing
logical that says

01:30:28.760 --> 01:30:31.510
the daughters, the
granddaughters,

01:30:31.510 --> 01:30:35.030
and the subsequent
descendants of Eve

01:30:35.030 --> 01:30:38.530
had to stick to any
particular set of males

01:30:38.530 --> 01:30:40.790
they were associated
with at the time

01:30:40.790 --> 01:30:45.290
or location of
Mitochondrial Eve.

01:30:45.290 --> 01:30:49.910
But wasn't it the male
line, the Y-chromosome Adam,

01:30:49.910 --> 01:30:51.440
that was earlier?

01:30:51.440 --> 01:30:55.445
Yes, it goes back
earlier, exactly.

01:30:55.445 --> 01:30:56.810
Possibly.

01:30:56.810 --> 01:30:57.640
Well, yes.

01:30:57.640 --> 01:30:59.040
It could intersect at one point.

01:30:59.040 --> 01:30:59.540
That's true.

01:30:59.540 --> 01:31:01.657
Yes, I mean, there's
still a range

01:31:01.657 --> 01:31:02.990
of error estimates on the dates.

01:31:02.990 --> 01:31:03.920
Intersect exactly, so
intersect at one point.

01:31:03.920 --> 01:31:04.660
It could at one point.

01:31:04.660 --> 01:31:05.618
There's just one point.

01:31:05.618 --> 01:31:10.340
It is possible that
they can be united.

01:31:10.340 --> 01:31:11.660
